headline: Dominion Energy Announces Third-Quarter 2025 Results
summary: RICHMOND, Va., October 31, 2025--Dominion Energy, Inc. (NYSE: D), today announced unaudited net income determined in accordance with Generally Accepted Accounting Principles (GAAP or reported earnings) for the three months ended Sept. 30, 2025, of $1.0 billion ($1.16 per share) compared with net income of $934 million ($1.09 per share) for the same period in 2024.
